  "text": "2) Detection and Extraction: In principal, we need to track flows of data in relevant APIs, and several static analysis frameworks exist to track data flows in Android apps. Nevertheless, in our experience as well as according to recent studies, these tools may not perform as described in the relevant papers [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] . We therefore decided to implement our own lightweight analysis tailored to reconstruct web APIs in the code.",
